<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, a PDF version of the book is available for purchase from online retailers such as Amazon and Barnes &amp; Noble.</p>
<p><strong>Q: What have critics said about "The Story of English"?</strong></p>
<p><strong>A:</strong> The book has received widespread critical acclaim. The Guardian called it "a magisterial account of the English language," while The New York Times praised its "breadth, erudition, and wit."</p>